        },
        "accordion_minimum_spend": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "Is there a minimum spend for jewellery repairs?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Yes, due to the time and craftsmanship involved, we have a minimum charge of £30 for our repair services. This covers the specialist's time, minor materials, and use of professional equipment. We always provide a transparent quote before work begins.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_appointment": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "Do I need an appointment for a repair quote?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>While appointments are not strictly necessary for our {{ page.metafields.custom.location.value }} customers dropping in for straightforward repairs, we highly recommend contacting us beforehand. For complex restorations, booking a consultation ensures dedicated time with one of our specialists.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_timeframe": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "How long will my jewellery repair take?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>The timeframe depends on the complexity of the work. Simple repairs like standard resizing or chain soldering usually take a few days, while intricate stone matching or restorations take longer. We will provide an estimated timeframe during your initial assessment.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_get_to_you": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "How do I get my jewellery to you?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>You are always welcome to visit us in Chichester. Alternatively, we can arrange a secure, insured postal service or a personal collection from your home in {{ page.metafields.custom.location.value }} for high-value items.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "accordion_not_from_griffin",
